019package org.jdrupes.vmoperator.runner.qemu.events;
020
021/**
022 * Signals that the connection to the Qemu monitor socket has been
023 * established successfully.
024 */
025public class MonitorReady extends MonitorEvent {
026
027    /**
028     * Instantiates a new monitor ready.
029     */
030    public MonitorReady() {
031        super(Kind.READY, null);
032    }
033
034}
